NOTE ON THIRD-PARTY COMPONENTS

This repository bundles several third-party ROS 2 packages under `src/`,
each retaining its own original license (see the LICENSE file inside each
package's directory):

- `src/teb_local_planner/`      — BSD-3-Clause / Apache-2.0 (see subfolder)
- `src/m-explore-ros2/`         — BSD-3-Clause
- `src/costmap_converter/`      — BSD-3-Clause

The MIT license above applies only to the original code written for this
project (task_manager, Docker/launch configuration, scripts, and
